notes: Conditional logic via Python control flow

pipeline_summary.name: Backup Strategy Selector
pipeline_summary.description: Comprehensive pipeline that selects a backup strategy (full or incremental) based on the day of week, using a branchmerge pattern.

components.name: Start Backup Process
components.description: Initialises the backup workflow and triggers the date check step.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies; starts the DAG.

components.name: Determine Backup Strategy
components.description: Evaluates the execution date to decide whether to run a full backup (Saturday) or an incremental backup (weekday).

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the start task completes successfully.

components.name: Perform Full Backup
components.description: Executes a simulated full database backup; runs only on Saturdays.

upstream_policy.description: Triggered when the splitter selects the full backup branch.

components.name: Perform Incremental Backup
components.description: Executes a simulated incremental backup of changed data; runs on weekdays.

upstream_policy.description: Triggered when the splitter selects the incremental backup branch.

components.name: Verify Backup
components.description: Validates backup integrity and completeness after either full or incremental backup.

upstream_policy.description: Runs when at least one of the backup branches succeeds (trigger_rule='none_failed_min_one_success').

components.name: Finalize Backup
components.description: Marks the backup workflow as complete after verification.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful verification of the backup.

description.default: Comprehensive pipeline that selects a backup strategy (full or incremental) based on the day of week, using a branchmerge pattern.
